                            <comment id="15560053" author="cziegeler" created="Sun, 9 Oct 2016 14:15:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for reporting, it&apos;s actually slightly worse, the DS XML schema uses a sequence of&lt;br/&gt;
property&lt;br/&gt;
properties&lt;br/&gt;
service&lt;br/&gt;
reference&lt;br/&gt;
implementation&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;which means that usually service always comes before implementation - if the generated XML is valid&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So I think we should a) fix the generation of the XML to have the correct order and b) make the read independent of any order&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15560071" author="cziegeler" created="Sun, 9 Oct 2016 14:25:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=enterit&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;enterit&quot;&gt;enterit&lt;/a&gt; I&apos;ve committed  a potential fix in rev 1763983, could you please give this a try?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
